Help me?

12
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:14,270
Maybe they don't speak English.

13
00:01:14,270 --> 00:01:17,170
Japan, Japan, Japan, Japan.

14
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:21,950
Welcome! How can I help you?

15
00:01:21,950 --> 00:01:23,810
 (You're getting what you got last time, right?) 

16
00:01:23,810 --> 00:01:25,460
 (Yes) 

17
00:01:25,460 --> 00:01:27,830
 (So why are you taking so long? Do you want whipped cream?) 

18
00:01:27,830 --> 00:01:29,220
 (Of course) 

19
00:01:29,220 --> 00:01:30,520
 (Don't forget, get an extra espresso shot) 

20
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:32,620
 (Are you crazy? That's expensive. Just drink it normally.) 

21
00:01:32,620 --> 00:01:34,720
 (I thought you were going to use reward points anyway.) 

22
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,740
 (You cheapskate!) 

23
00:01:35,740 --> 00:01:37,490
Hello, excuse me.

24
00:01:37,490 --> 00:01:40,180
Excuse me. Um...

25
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:44,590
If you can write down what you would like...

26
00:01:44,590 --> 00:01:49,250
I would like a large double espresso frappe with extra whipped cream and caramel syrup.

27
00:01:49,250 --> 00:01:54,010
And a large mocha java chip frappe, please.

28
00:01:54,010 --> 00:01:55,790
Yes.

29
00:01:55,790 --> 00:01:57,700
You got that, right?

30
00:01:57,700 --> 00:02:00,560
 (- Did you get the extra shot?)  
 - Double espresso with whipped cream...

31
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:03,280
Excuse me. Could I get an extra shot in the double espresso frappe?

32
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,890
- Extra shot. 
 - Extra shot.

33
00:02:04,890 --> 00:02:06,270
Yes.

34
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:22,490
 (Why do you want me to wear this? It's useless.) 

35
00:02:22,490 --> 00:02:24,400
You don't get it.

36
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:27,290
You need this so cars don't honk at you.

37
00:02:27,290 --> 00:02:29,030
They know you won't hear them,

38
00:02:29,030 --> 00:02:31,940
so they just go around you.

39
00:02:34,340 --> 00:02:36,440
You also look cool.

40
